30:52.880 --> 30:56.089
<i>I presumed that
And you never told him what happened?</i>

30:56.240 --> 31:01.371
No. I had bruises all over my neck.
Really bad headaches.

31:01.520 --> 31:02.931
My voice was hoarse.

31:03.800 --> 31:06.041
So I simply stopped seeing him.

31:07.080 --> 31:10.402
Rose, I understand
it will be a difficult conversation...

31:12.600 --> 31:14.728
But there are bigger issues.

31:16.840 --> 31:18.842
I know.

31:21.320 --> 31:23.322
- Hello?
- I'm here.

31:24.360 --> 31:27.807
<i>Talk to him tonight.
Come and see me tomorrow.</i>

31:30.480 --> 31:33.006
- I can come in at noon.
<i>- I'll see you then.</i>

31:47.920 --> 31:50.207
<i>He's written and he's phoned</i>

31:50.840 --> 31:55.926
