was part of Olson's time line.

51:24.160 --> 51:26.811
So the marks went unaccounted for
in my report.

51:30.400 --> 51:32.402
I'm surprised by that.

51:33.120 --> 51:35.122
By What?

51:36.800 --> 51:38.802
By Eastwood withholding that.

51:42.200 --> 51:44.202
You didn't ask him to?

51:48.000 --> 51:50.002
No.

51:51.560 --> 51:53.369
Hm...

51:54.400 --> 51:57.404
So was it you? Made those marks?

52:04.680 --> 52:06.682
They don't feel sharp.

52:07.680 --> 52:09.682
No.

52:11.000 --> 52:13.002
Not any more.

52:47.000 --> 52:49.002
How did you come to meet him?

52:51.040 --> 52:54.169
I saw him, on the street...

52:55.040 --> 52:57.042
"at a crime scene.

52:58.200 --> 53:02.808
I thought I would be in Belfast for...
