53:10.400 --> 53:13.882
I'm sorry he's dead...I really am.

53:16.560 --> 53:18.562
But it was one night.

53:19.880 --> 53:21.848
It didn't mean anything.

53:25.000 --> 53:28.288
Excuse me, ma'am.
