- I'll show you.

56:50.320 --> 56:52.721
- Where's Mummy sleeping?
- In there.

57:18.800 --> 57:20.928
Hm, that's nice.

57:25.440 --> 57:27.442
I'm sorry.

57:29.520 --> 57:31.522
Me too.

57:57.800 --> 58:01.600
I want you to come with me now.
I wanna talk to you.

58:04.360 --> 58:06.567
I don't wanna have to hurt you, Rose.

58:07.440 --> 58:09.761
I don't wanna have to hurt your beautiful family.

58:09.920 --> 58:11.410
But I will...

58:12.600 --> 58:15.365
I will if you scream or cry out when I release you.

58:16.800 --> 58:18.802
Do you understand?

